dct_title_s: Delaware River Harbor Lines: Pennsylvania Shore from mouth of Schuykill River to Greenwich Point, New Jersey Shore from Red Bank to Newton Creek
dct_description_sm: Map shows the area along the Delaware River from Red Bank to Newton Creek in New Jersey and the Schuykill River to Greenwich Point in Pennsylvania.

Map shows parts of League Island, Howell Cove, Big Timber Creek, Schuylkill River, Horse Shoe Shoal, and Newton Creek. Map also has detailed sketches showing locations of stations and a table of course, bearings, and distances
